{"tid":2143904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳軍車不堪一擊致傷亡 東風稱造謠","createTime":"2020-08-07T10:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T10:57:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3659a759b18b2b996a5169bd680039c9f0a140ac","tid":2143904,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200807/4NYT4HTGTP5Q7K2QUD26S6C65I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200807%2F4NYT4HTGTP5Q7K2QUD26S6C65I%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=139d9e1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200807%2F4NYT4HTGTP5Q7K2QUD26S6C65I%2F&h=0847a75c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200807/4NYT4HTGTP5Q7K2QUD26S6C65I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n傳軍車不堪一擊致傷亡 東風稱造謠<br />\n<br />\n中印6月爆發邊境衝突後，中國軍車製造商東風汽車的兩名高層被扣查，網絡瘋傳兩人受賄採購劣質鋼材作軍車原材料，導致軍人在衝突中傷亡。其子公司東風越野汽車昨「闢謠」，稱涉事網民已承認自己散佈謠言，並寫下悔過書。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GFivPF1-CUk8DG9T2z8rsrxldXI=/640x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GWP3VR6LUF6QW5LNKFCZ3SQMN4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGFivPF1-CUk8DG9T2z8rsrxldXI%3D%2F640x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGWP3VR6LUF6QW5LNKFCZ3SQMN4.jpg&h=22f62444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n月前衝突中，有印軍攻擊解放軍軍車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「防彈鋼變劣質鋼」<br />\n<br />\n東風汽車集團在5月底至6月初，接連宣佈特種裝備事業部（東風越野車有限公司）副總經理周旺生，以及東風汽車集團前副總工程師陳建賢涉嫌嚴重違紀違法接受審查。一個月內兩位高層落馬，令不少人猜測當中原因。<br />\n<br />\n網民「天佑眾生」在本月初於微信群中，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n內媒昨指，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國只有兩間汽車央企，東風汽車是其中一間。內媒報道周旺生自2011年起已是公司領導層，2018年起負責管理和營運東風公司的軍事物品，陳建賢更是東風「猛士」車型的核心研發者之一。<br />\n<br />\n湖北紀委/環球時報"}]}